{"tid":2229302,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"拿玻里因防疫原因無法鬥祖記 或直接被判輸0-3！","createTime":"2020-10-04T09:36:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-05T00:12:08.000Z","uid":173952,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"3a5d3527fffa7863549ca46737d764df028dab74","tid":2229302,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T09:36:36.000Z","msg":"據記者迪馬斯奧消息，拿玻里受防疫情況影響，無法前往作客拖連奴參加本輪與祖記的比賽。隨後祖記與意甲官方都宣佈，今場比賽將會如期進行。因此根據規則，拿玻里很有可能被直接判0-3負。<br />\n<br />\n  據悉拿玻里因為防疫原因前往作客拖連奴的行程受阻，但意大利媒體最新報導指出，拿玻里當地衛生部門並沒有禁止拿玻里的出行，只是建議他們隔離訓練，最終是否前往作客比賽由球會自己決定。<br />\n<br />\n  依據意甲聯盟規定，每支球隊單賽季有一次豁免權，就是一支球隊一週內至少10名球員新冠檢測呈陽性，那麼他們可以申請比賽延期進行。但目前拿玻里並不符合此項規定，隊內有史連斯基（Piotr Zielinski）和艾馬斯（Elif Elmas）兩名球隊新冠檢測呈陽性。<br />\n<br />\n  歐洲足協的規則中，如果一支球隊有13名球員（其中有1名門將），那麼就具備比賽條件，未出場比賽就被自動判0-3負。"},{"pid":"6d8e7a6d73045f5e217a8da5b3943ab2d2249e3d","tid":2229302,"uid":190158,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T09:37:21.000Z","msg":"又黑"},{"pid":"b4c7b82c33d96cca186793ba3355d165ac483829","tid":2229302,"uid":217450,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"6d8e7a6d73045f5e217a8da5b3943ab2d2249e3d","tid":2229302,"uid":190158,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T09:37:21.000Z","msg":"又黑"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T09:39:42.000Z","msg":"拿玻里可自行決定是否作賽喎<br />\n黑乜？"},{"pid":"b29e4d85f8f573a17a2bcd3d8790ebffc4fb4cfa","tid":2229302,"uid":173952,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T09:42:24.000Z","msg":"阿朗無得刷入波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d136c75aadaa4354c3101d790da7caea2361dbae","tid":2229302,"uid":34571,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b29e4d85f8f573a17a2bcd3d8790ebffc4fb4cfa","tid":2229302,"uid":173952,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T09:42:24.000Z","msg":"阿朗無得刷入波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T09:43:31.000Z","msg":"果三球計佢入"},{"pid":"6d0b263f58a82947537ecfea4aa022fc18bd1aef","tid":2229302,"uid":8951,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T09:45:11.000Z","msg":"事但啦<br />\n最後都係祖記拎意甲"},{"pid":"c055060bc1e533c46253c080291199ce5415779f","tid":2229302,"uid":33418,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T09:51:24.000Z","msg":"照踢囉，兩隊一齊攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1718a911d4310b2940af44a2f5085607945f743d","tid":2229302,"uid":20473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c055060bc1e533c46253c080291199ce5415779f","tid":2229302,"uid":33418,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T09:51:24.000Z","msg":"照踢囉，兩隊一齊攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T09:52:22.000Z","msg":"齊齊攬阿朗<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e3b8b83f63ad08297644e4a4176fc47c82838c3","tid":2229302,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T18:59:34.000Z","msg":"意足協確定：今晚比賽必須進行，沒有任何規例規定這個情況要停舼。<br />\n球員和球証應該要在球場等候45分鐘，如果對手沒有出現，將被判3:0勝出。"},{"pid":"1cded4fed5e8dae8fdc8288c5d35e7bfb3e18503","tid":2229302,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T19:31:52.000Z","msg":"香港時間10月5日2時45分（意大利當地時間4日20時45分），意甲第3輪原定祖雲達斯主場迎戰拿玻里。拿玻里沒有到達球場，祖記等待45分鐘後，將被判3比0勝出。<br />\n<br />\n3分已袋"},{"pid":"f95892193f79baa8b3e42f0621da66247713621d","tid":2229302,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T23:45:40.000Z","msg":"無人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />個個抽雙紅<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d4fec1abd8a24eeff09f1b980b58c62e3e71c9d","tid":2229302,"uid":1734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f95892193f79baa8b3e42f0621da66247713621d","tid":2229302,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T23:45:40.000Z",